            "author_association": "NONE",
            "body": "I've been running with this:\n\n```diff\n--- a/src/nvim/msgpack_rpc/channel.c\n+++ b/src/nvim/msgpack_rpc/channel.c\n@@ -507,7 +507,7 @@ static void rpc_close_event(void **argv)\n       }\n     }\n     if (!channel->detach) {\n-      if (channel->streamtype == kChannelStreamProc && ui_client_error_exit < 0) {\n+      if ((channel->streamtype == kChannelStreamProc || channel->streamtype == kChannelStreamStdio) && ui_client_error_exit < 0\n) {\n         // Wait for the embedded server to exit instead of exiting immediately,\n         // as it's necessary to get the server's exit code in on_proc_exit().\n       } else {\n```\n\nwhich gets 301 tests passing, but the tests eventually time out.",
